  "prompt": "What are the services provided by Five Boro Mold Specialist?",
  "response": "Five Boro Mold Specialist offers a range of services primarily focused on mold inspection, testing, and remediation. Their services typically include:\n\n1. **Mold Inspection**: Comprehensive assessments to identify the presence of mold in residential or commercial properties.\n\n2. **Mold Testing**: Professional testing to determine the type and extent of mold contamination.\n\n3. **Mold Remediation**: Safe and effective removal of mold and implementation of measures to prevent future growth.\n\n4. **Water Damage Restoration**: Services to address and mitigate damage caused by water leaks or flooding, which can lead to mold growth.\n\n5. **Indoor Air Quality Testing**: Evaluations to assess air quality and the presence of mold spores or other contaminants.\n\n6. **Consultation and Prevention Advice**: Guidance on maintaining a mold-free environment and addressing underlying moisture issues.\n\nIt's always best to check their official website or contact them directly for the most current and detailed information regarding their services.",
